data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS: HIGHEST & BEST BY SATURDAY, 5 PM, 08.29.20. Welcome to this improved, move-in ready home in Deer Creek North! This quiet, established neighborhood boasts quick access to I-35 and the shopping and conveniences of both Crowley and Fort Worth. Sweet curb appeal opens up to a freshly painted interior, new laminate flooring, decorative backsplash in the kitchen plus a new stainless steel gas stove and oven. All carpet has been recently replaced. All bedrooms are upstairs, including a spacious master suite with a bathroom boasting large garden tub, separate shower, and huge closet. Community pool, park, trails, and ponds to enjoy nearby! Welcome home!
